Thanks, Dennis! I really enjoyed this project. I am going to add the backend also. I was having a problem with new notes not showing up until I refreshed the page. 
I see that you were able to get yours working, but mine didn't, so it wasn't lagging. I researched it and it was a hot reload issue. So I had to add an .env file with FAST_REFRESH=false in the file and that fixed the issue. Posting this in case anyone else had this issue.
